title: Help Me, My Love 1964 (Italian cinema, Romantic Comedy) Colorized Movie

sources.title: Help Me, My Love 1964 (Italian cinema, Romantic Comedy) Colorized Movie
sources.description:
Romantic comedy-drama about a husband (Sordi) who is jealous of his wife's (Vitti) infatuation with a Professor.

Original title: Amore mio aiutami  (1964)

Black & White version; https://youtu.be/dKZ5Mq70vu4

Director: Alberto Sordi
Writers: Rodolfo Sonego, Alberto Sordi, Tullio Pinelli
Stars: Alberto Sordi, Monica Vitti, Silvano Tranquilli
Genres: Colorized classics, Italian cinema, Comedy, Drama, Romance

This film is subtitled in many languages.
